com.vector.cfg.gen.core.bswmdmodel

Interface GIHasContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GIHasParameterAccessFunctions, GIModelObject, IViewedModelObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GIChoiceContainer, GIContainer, GIModuleConfiguration

    @NotThreadSafe
 @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
public interface GIHasContainer
extends GIModelObject, GIHasParameterAccessFunctions
    Base interface of bswmd model objects that has container.

    All method parameters must be non-null unless documented otherwise.

      • getSubContainers

        @PublishedMethod
java.util.List<GIContainer> getSubContainers(DefRef defRef)
        Returns all sub-containers with the specified definition-name in the same order as they are stored in the MDF model.

        If no container was found, the collection is EMPTY and not null, so you must not check against null. No exception is thrown, if no or one element was found.

        Parameters:
        defRef - The DefRef of the subcontainer.
        Returns:
        A unmodifiable List of containers for the request.
        Throws:
        McaDefinitionUndefinedException -
        • if the DefinitionRef is invalid
        McaWrongTypeException -
        • if the retrieved elements has the wrong type
